# This is a Turing Machine coded in python
It is designed so that I could teach about Turing Machines.
I was not particularly happy with the existing ones so I decided to make my own.
It is designed to be easy-ish to use while remaining in a single file so that it can be used in many free online compilers.

You are free to use this program:
To use it you must modify the program at the begining of the main.py file, that holds the Turing Machine rule set and starting conditions